Date: Thu, 19 Mar 2026 12:27:21 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: global Tab navigation + auto-select for ALL inputs
 across entire app

- Created client/src/hooks/useTabNavigation.ts
- Tab moves forward through all visible inputs in DOM order
- Shift+Tab moves backwards
- Number inputs auto-select text on focus (click or tab)
- Works on every page: sales, purchase, items, parties, agents, companies, etc.
- Single global init in main.tsx - no per-page changes needed
